author: Ubisoft
description:
Experience the feel of GP Explorer - The Last Race in The Crew Motorfest from October 1 to 7! Get ready to play a special in-game event, the Pole Position - Powered by Gp Explorer Summit, with 6 races inspired by the IRL competition. Try it to unlock a unique in-game vehicle based on the official livery of our team at the event - don't forget to support team The Crew Motorfest, feat. Ludwig and Michael Reeves, on October 4-5!
 
More info: https://thecrewgame.com/GPExplorer25-event

About The Crew Motorfest:
Welcome to Motorfest! Discover the evergreen festival featuring the best experiences car culture has to offer. Complete your ultimate action driving bucket list through a series of tailor-made races, themed events, and other unique challenges. Explore the vibrant island of O’ahu in Hawaii alone or with your crew. Whatever the way you enjoy cars and driving, there is something in there for you!

#Ubisoft #TheCrew #TheCrewMotorfest

Learn more about Ubisoft: www.ubisoftgroup.com

author: Ubisoft
description:
“You’re a hard man to reach, Sam Fisher.” 2 weeks until TOM CLANCY’S SPLINTER CELL: DEATHWATCH.

From Derek Kolstad, the writer behind the John Wick franchise, comes the first-ever adaptation of the acclaimed stealth video game franchise, Tom Clancy’s Splinter Cell. After a long absence from the field, legendary agent Sam Fisher (Liev Schreiber) is drawn back into action when a wounded young operative (Kirby Howell-Baptiste) seeks his help. TOM CLANCY'S SPLINTER CELL: DEATHWATCH will be available worldwide on October 14 on Netflix.

About Ubisoft Film & Television

Ubisoft Film & Television’s mission is to bring Ubisoft’s award-winning games into new areas of entertainment and to create original stories set in the world, culture, and community of gaming. All four seasons of the division’s first original series, Mythic Quest, and spin-off anthology series Side Quest are available to stream globally on Apple TV+.
